title: Dr Noodles
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, International, Japanese, Thai, Fast food, Take-out, Fusion, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast-paced and friendly noodle bar part of a franchise chain. Choose from wheat noodles or rice. Comes with vegetables. Choose sauce (all vegetarian sauces are vegan except for honey). Vegetarian listed, staff are vegan aware and provide options.
